//purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2014/12/brainwash-using-real-data.html","ref":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-7023728249858654098","source":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/7023728249858654098","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2014年12月26日 16:05:00"}]},{"gd$etag":"W/\"D0UCSX84fyp7ImA9XRVaEE8.\"","id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-755372406135798660"},"published":{"$t":"2015-08-08T17:14:28.137+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2015-08-08T17:14:28.137+08:00"},"app$edited":{"xmlns$app":"http://www.w3.org/2007/app","$t":"2015-08-08T17:14:28.137+08:00"},"title":{"$t":"TO 二翔子\n（你这条留言被 Google 误判为垃圾广告，刚才被俺恢复出来）\n\n多谢分享你写的博文..."},"content":{"type":"html","$t":"TO 二翔子<br />（你这条留言被 Google 误判为垃圾广告，刚才被俺恢复出来）<br /><br />多谢分享你写的博文 :)<br />前几天有个读者在留言中推荐 Disconnect Search，不知道是不是你？<br />当时俺尝试了一下，发现这玩意儿比另一个匿名搜索 StartPage 好用。"},"link":[{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/8685762110847516884/comments/default/755372406135798660?v=2"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/8685762110847516884/comments/default/755372406135798660?v=2"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2015/08/gfw-news.html?showComment=1439025268137#c755372406135798660","title":"2015年8月翻墙快报"},{"rel":"related","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/8685762110847516884/comments/default/5909277395641614171?v=2"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg?cache=36c4cca294ae50025f1c139a5907df5d"}}],"thr$in-reply-to":{"xmlns$thr":"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2015/08/gfw-news.html","ref":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-8685762110847516884","source":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/8685762110847516884","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2015年8月8日 17:14:00"}]},{"gd$etag":"W/\"DkUNRXo_fip7ImA9XBFUGE0.\"","id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-6240272786417978239"},"published":{"$t":"2019-12-31T22:58:14.446+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2019-12-31T22:58:14.446+08:00"},"app$edited":{"xmlns$app":"http://www.w3.org/2007/app","$t":"2019-12-31T22:58:14.446+08:00"},"title":{"$t":"TO 孟宇\n关于“择偶”\n这个问题确实比较“大”，比较发散，而且可以聊的点有很多。\n考虑到俺时间有限..."},"content":{"type":"html","$t":"TO 孟宇<br />关于“择偶”<br />这个问题确实比较“大”，比较发散，而且可以聊的点有很多。<br />考虑到俺时间有限，简单说几个点，肯定不全面，凑合着看。<br />（个人观点，仅供参考）<br /><br />========<br /><br />[b]1、价值观[/b]<br />首先，任何两个人的价值观，【不可能】完全一致。<br />但如果要考虑“择偶”，“价值观”的【差异】，要保持在一定的限度（差异不能太大）<br />比如说：一个“虔诚的基督徒”碰上一个“坚定的无神论者”，那就会有很多【价值观冲突】。<br /><br />俺曾经在网上看到某人分享的“相亲经验”，其中提到说（大意）<br />[quote]<br />相亲时，先问对方两个问题：<br />1、如何看待中共？<br />2、如何看待中医？<br /><br />通过这两个问题，可以直接过滤掉 90% 以上的人。<br />然后再与剩下不到 10% 的人进一步聊。<br />[/quote]<br />不得不说，这两个问题，确实具有很高的【筛选度】 :)<br /><br /><br />[b]2、性格[/b]<br />很多人把“性格”与“价值观”混淆。<br />这是两个不同的维度。<br />有些婚后的冲突是由于“价值观因素”，有些是由于“性格因素”<br />“价值观”导致的冲突，通常是由于【差异】引起滴；<br />而“性格”导致的冲突，就【不一定】是由于“差异”引起滴。<br />比如说：某种类型的性格，与任何人都难以相处。<br />再比如说：如果两个人都是上述这种性格，虽然差异化【很小】，但冲突反而会更剧烈。<br /><br /><br />[b]3、基于时间的检验[/b]<br />再结合本文聊的主题，俺建议：交往【足够长】的时间，再结婚。<br />至于多长的时间算【足够长】，这个因人而异，俺【无法】给出某个通用的标准。<br /><br />很多“价值观 ＆ 性格”导致的冲突，假以时日，总是能感觉到。<br />“结婚前意识到问题”总好过“结婚后发现”。<br /><br /><br />[b]4、【不】要刻意掩饰缺点[/b]<br />结婚前，很多人总是会刻意掩饰缺点。<br />这【没】必要，甚至有害。<br />坦率地让对方知道自己的某些缺点，反而是有好处滴。<br />这可以降低“成本”。<br />还是那句话——“在婚前发现缺点”总好过在“婚后发现”<br /><br /><br />[b]5、避免【选择性失察】[/b]<br />关于【选择性失察】，俺已经在多篇博文中聊过，甚至在本文的评论区也聊过（15楼62单元）。<br />恋爱中的男女，容易出现“情人眼里出西施”的情况。这就是典型的【选择性失察】。"},"link":[{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4457275194674072144/comments/default/6240272786417978239?v=2"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4457275194674072144/comments/default/6240272786417978239?v=2"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/12/Time-and-Life.html?showComment=1577804294446#c6240272786417978239","title":"时间与人生&#8212;&#8212;跨入本世纪20年代的随想"},{"rel":"related","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4457275194674072144/comments/default/1953382193238358504?v=2"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg?cache=36c4cca294ae50025f1c139a5907df5d"}}],"thr$in-reply-to":{"xmlns$thr":"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/12/Time-and-Life.html","ref":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-4457275194674072144","source":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/4457275194674072144","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2019年12月31日 22:58:00"}]},{"gd$etag":"W/\"AkAEQXc-cCp7ImA9Wh9TF08.\"","id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1379487611229758906"},"published":{"$t":"2014-01-26T17:31:40.958+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2014-01-26T17:31:40.958+08:00"},"app$edited":{"xmlns$app":"http://www.w3.org/2007/app","$t":"2014-01-26T17:31:40.958+08:00"},"title":{"$t":"TO 1单元的网友\n关于“避孕套和艾滋病”\n首先，艾滋病病毒是无法穿透传统乳胶安全套的——即使比艾滋..."},"content":{"type":"html","$t":"TO 1单元的网友<br />关于“避孕套和艾滋病”<br />首先，艾滋病病毒是无法穿透传统乳胶安全套的——即使比艾滋病病毒小很多的乙肝病毒也无法穿透（网上有传言说可以穿透，是误传）<br />其次，戴套可以提高安全系数，但【不是】百分百安全（因为有很多人使用不当）<br /><br />如果担心艾滋病，最好是别去嫖娼。"},"link":[{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2701782986490415166/comments/default/1379487611229758906?v=2"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2701782986490415166/comments/default/1379487611229758906?v=2"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2014/01/dns.html?showComment=1390728700958#c1379487611229758906","title":"扫盲 DNS 原理&#65292;兼谈&#8220;域名劫持&#8221;和&#8220;域名欺骗/域名污染&#8221;"},{"rel":"related","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2701782986490415166/comments/default/2714977924412384674?v=2"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg?cache=36c4cca294ae50025f1c139a5907df5d"}}],"thr$in-reply-to":{"xmlns$thr":"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2014/01/dns.html","ref":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-2701782986490415166","source":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/2701782986490415166","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2014年1月26日 17:31:00"}]},{"gd$etag":"W/\"CEcHQnw5cSp7ImA9XBRSGE8.\"","id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-3253270531616213302